-Eyes on me. And… -Yep. And, go!

164
00:12:16,620 --> 00:12:17,450
‎真棒
Oi, very good!

165
00:12:17,540 --> 00:12:20,580
‎別以為冰箱里 ‎會有東西憑空出現 湯姆
Don't think anything new's gonna appear in there, Tom.

166
00:12:20,660 --> 00:12:23,580
‎很好 你會把自己轉暈的
-Very good. -You're gonna make yourself dizzy.

167
00:12:23,660 --> 00:12:24,830
‎我知道
-I know!

168
00:12:25,410 --> 00:12:27,700
‎-打到你嘍  ‎-喂 別胡鬧
-Got you! -Oi! Cut it out!

169
00:12:27,790 --> 00:12:30,290
‎-我接受采訪的話 有錢賺嗎  ‎-不夠多
-Would they pay me for interviews? -Not enough for repairs.

170
00:12:30,370 --> 00:12:33,000
‎-杰西卡沃森的冒險就在她的家人… ‎-看
-Jessica Watson's adventure… -Jess, look!

171
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:36,910
…收拾好行囊 ‎開啟穿越澳洲之旅的那一刻展開了
‎…began when her family packed up their lives and traveled across Australia.

172
00:12:37,410 --> 00:12:40,160
‎當她讀到獨立航海人杰西馬丁的書時
When she read solo sailor Jesse Martin's book,

173
00:12:40,250 --> 00:12:43,620
