00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:52,870
‎師從臭名昭著的水手本布萊恩特 ‎踏上了艱苦的逐夢之路
with infamous sailor Ben Bryant, and worked rigorously to pursue her dream.

176
00:12:52,950 --> 00:12:56,330
‎但她的夢想是否演變成了噩夢
But has that dream turned into a nightmare?

177
00:12:56,410 --> 00:12:57,580
‎劇情大反轉啊
Whoa! Plot twist!

178
00:12:57,660 --> 00:12:58,790
‎兒童福利團體
Child welfare groups are calling

179
00:12:58,870 --> 00:13:01,450
‎說這是不負責任和危險的嘗試
the attempt by the schoolgirl irresponsible and dangerous.

